Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:06.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:10.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:19.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Savannah's Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:23.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't this everyone's favorite Takahashi?\N  -Everyone loves him
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:25.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:27.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it's not right to say "no such thing"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:34.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We have previously verified that it is easy to leave an artist alone on location
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did it several times \N -3 times
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:37.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Panther's Ogata\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tram?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:44.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the other side of the road crossing was the film crew
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:46.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When the tram passed, the people were gone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:50.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Most unpleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:54.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, we bring you a spin on this idea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory i've brought is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:02.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Waking up in the morning at your travel destination to find everyone else missing is quite sad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:04.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cry. I'm going to cry. \N -It's hard to top
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What else do you need to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:10.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time the person is left behind on a private trip
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:11.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:14.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Imagine getting up in the morning and finding yourself alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:15.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What would you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:18.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, you'd call someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:20.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd call
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:22.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First you'd call them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:24.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Cookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'd think, "No, I'll just keep waiting"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:29.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:31.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait until my flesh disappears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:33.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only the skeleton remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.27,0:01:35.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is my fault, I shouldn't have asked you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:37.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:59.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Waking up in the morning at your travel destination to find everyone else missing is quite sad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:58.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So sad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, the first scene is camping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:05.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a bit scary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The target is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:17.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, this time not only the camping partners who came together are missing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:23.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All the camping supplies except for the tent that he is sleeping in are also taken away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:29.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The setting is to wake up in the morning and find themselves completely alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:34.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:38.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The long-awaited camping trip of the Ogata Army begins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has something interesting happened to you recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:45.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In fact, 2~3 months ago I went on a trip
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:51.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Commandante Ishii, KAZMA and I, and Attack Nishimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We booked random accommodation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This will do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And went to a hot spring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably, Tsuyoshi Nagabuchi was there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The real guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awesome.  \N-Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't give me an unexpectedly surprising story!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was there for his health
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems that the lower half of his body is also quite strong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I forgot to look at his knob
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Show me. That's the most important thing, right, you guy?\N  Forgot to look at the knob...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear what kind of knob he has\N  -Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:26.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A million unexpected Nagabuchi anecdotes got the group all excited
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:30.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They did not go to sleep until 2:00 am
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good night  \N-Goodnight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, 3 hours later
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, who's out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In order not to wake him up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata slowly starts to crawl out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:08.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive, he's out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:15.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the two people in the next tent get up quietly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And quickly began to retreat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:23.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't put it all away, it's not funny
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:26.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then, the other tent is carried away untouched
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.91,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Preparation work completed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Waking up would be scary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next step is just to wait for him to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:38.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata looks like he's been up all night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:42.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, after an hour and a half there is no sign of him waking up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The time came at 6:50
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:47.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What will be the reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's almost 7:00
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks so sleepy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eyes swollen like copper bells
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not the face of the setter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:59.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The alarm clock will go off
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here is the perfect opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This will definitely wake him up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:08.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We go home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:08.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:19.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:26.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's up, he's up, he's up, he's up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, he wakes up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:38.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He first notices the person next to him is gone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably dumbfounded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:49.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course you'd react like this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd look beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one at all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,All silent
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Single camping
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why're you looking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:07.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, we aren't there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:10.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey, why is there no one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You think they'll be there if you look again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really double-checking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're not there, how can we be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The campsite has been searched for all the way back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:28.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, there is no sign of anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, even the tent is gone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:34.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Later, he tries calling Ogata's phone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely won't answer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:43.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why... ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:46.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thinks he did something wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did I say something that excessive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:58.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He thinks he's been left behind because of a slip of the tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:02.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:06.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then... disillusioned
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:11.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For some reason he lies on the river bank for more than 30 minutes in anger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This was followed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:19.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pushing against a tree stump
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:25.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And bathing in the river with his clothes on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.53,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems to be quite enjoyable
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:31.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:36.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Head buried in the tent and shouting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All kinds of peculiar behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:45.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This solo camping lasted for three hours
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At last, he begins putting things in order
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And packs the tent away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To leave the campground
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:59.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For the taxi that he calls
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:03.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The program team sent a pre-prepared vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One-person camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, originally four people came together
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know why the other 3 people are missing in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:14.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They seem to have gone back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not only are the people gone, but the camping tools are also gone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am really too miserable
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:24.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,30 minutes to the nearest station
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:32.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ogata!
