Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.51,0:28:11.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The anaconda vice
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.69,0:28:15.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wrists and neck are clamped in a death grip
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.46,0:28:18.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The original move of Tenzan Hiyoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.92,0:28:23.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Therefore, Tenzan will explain the move
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.55,0:28:27.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's coming. Then I'll answer it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.79,0:28:30.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah... hello
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.42,0:28:31.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello~
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.96,0:28:33.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.86,0:28:36.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm Tenzan Hiroyoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.66,0:28:39.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am a professional wrestler
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.23,0:28:40.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Aika, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.40,0:28:42.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Aika The Spy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.43,0:28:45.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, next
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.00,0:28:48.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say this move
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.54,0:28:51.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is Miyuki there?\N  -She's next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.19,0:28:54.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems so suspicious! \N -Very true
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.71,0:29:00.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, can you lie on your back, Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.80,0:29:03.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary looking but softly spoken
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.96,0:29:09.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Akin to some new type of telephone fraud, Tenzan explains
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.36,0:29:16.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Aika should be pressing against Miyuki's upper body
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.40,0:29:17.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.57,0:29:19.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I've done it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.94,0:29:23.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.84,0:29:28.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please grab her right wrist
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.08,0:29:34.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Grab the right wrist with the left hand, right?\N  -Yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.88,0:29:41.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then, just like this, press on her
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.46,0:29:45.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pull hard in the direction of Miyuki's feet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.26,0:29:50.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hand clenched like you're trying to break her neck
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.27,0:29:54.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does it feel like the neck is going to break? \N -Stop! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.14,0:29:56.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It hurts, Aika, Aika
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.94,0:30:01.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It hurts!\N-How about the referee?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.48,0:30:03.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No? Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.55,0:30:04.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.38,0:30:06.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.35,0:30:10.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, OK Come on, it's good
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.05,0:30:11.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.79,0:30:18.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tenzan and Mameshiba no Taigun perfectly complete the move in 3 minutes and 49 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.88,0:30:21.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"OK Come on" is good
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.10,0:30:24.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final challengers are...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.49,0:30:25.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.05,0:30:29.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda Ueda
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.20,0:30:33.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,These two are challenged with the skill of...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.47,0:30:39.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,While clamping one of the opponent's legs
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.89,0:30:41.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lock the face upwards as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.34,0:30:46.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,STF - The step-over toehold with face-lock
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.81,0:30:47.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This looks so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.14,0:30:52.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The person in charge of explaining the technique is the creator, Chono Masahino
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.34,0:30:56.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am Chono
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.43,0:30:59.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.17,0:31:02.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First, please put the opponent down
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.31,0:31:03.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please let her lie down
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.31,0:31:04.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This way
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.41,0:31:10.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She down?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.45,0:31:12.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, already lying down
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.77,0:31:14.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So noisy
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.38,0:31:16.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then, Ueda is lying down... what're you called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.65,0:31:19.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm Oda \N-Oda
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.66,0:31:24.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda, please lift up Ueda's legs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.41,0:31:28.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But in fact, the original version is not two legs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.52,0:31:31.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Instead, only one leg is lifted to turn the person over
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.68,0:31:33.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's the beginning of this technique
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.52,0:31:37.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 3,0:31:37.84,0:31:39.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We aren't at the XXX
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.94,0:31:43.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wednesday... this isn't what I expected of Wednesday
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.48,0:31:46.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please take the left leg as the axis to turn the person over
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.35,0:31:47.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.08,0:31:49.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah it hurts, it's gonna break!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.15,0:31:52.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.39,0:31:50.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Accidentally said two legs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.01,0:31:54.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already doing it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.04,0:31:55.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.73,0:32:00.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda is lying face down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.53,0:32:03.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda is now sitting and has always been
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.03,0:32:05.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Sitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.94,0:32:09.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's Udea doing now? Lying down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.27,0:32:12.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda is sitting, Ueda is lying down
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.44,0:32:14.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, the name is a little difficult to distinguish
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.61,0:32:16.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry, I'm sorry, what...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.91,0:32:19.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're doing it to Ueda, right? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.48,0:32:21.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's no time for that, Chono
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.62,0:32:30.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda, please put your legs between her legs
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.19,0:32:32.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda uses her own legs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.80,0:32:34.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Both legs clamped
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.90,0:32:37.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No longer has anything to do with Ueda
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.93,0:32:41.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the middle of the leg
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.10,0:32:45.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The leg of Oda... ah not Oda, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.94,0:32:47.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does the leg look like now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.94,0:32:50.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The legs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.01,0:32:51.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's Oda's leg doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.58,0:32:53.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda is currently sitting
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.28,0:32:56.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah... \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:57.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just can't get Ueda's name out
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.22,0:33:00.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sitting? Wait... sitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.67,0:33:01.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already confused
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.92,0:33:02.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.53,0:33:05.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The caller is panicking
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.86,0:33:10.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda is down...facing downward and lying down?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.57,0:33:14.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda is still sitting, hasn't changed. \N -Eh? Sitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.37,0:33:17.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, is Ueda lying face down?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.97,0:33:19.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's lying face up
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.51,0:33:20.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah that's no good
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.96,0:33:27.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already in a state of affairs where the name and situation are confused
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.15,0:33:30.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Chono, time up
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.52,0:33:35.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this considered a failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.26,0:33:37.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's time to judge
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.39,0:33:40.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whose fault is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.46,0:33:43.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Instead of saying who... it's time
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.50,0:33:46.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,GOD DAMN!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.51,0:33:50.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, OK, thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.41,0:33:54.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H250EED&}In summary\N{\r}GOD DAMN!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.09,0:33:53.98,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.68,0:33:56.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The verification result is "God Damn!" what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.80,0:33:58.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a terrible ending
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.45,0:34:02.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Okay, OK", don't show us the place where his fire is extinguished
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.85,0:34:04.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Malicious editing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.38,0:34:09.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, it's confusing via phone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.23,0:34:10.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can't see each other at all
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.99,0:34:13.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If such a tradition existed, it would probably be very popular
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.76,0:34:16.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Store managers calling to send vulgar instructions to women...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.53,0:34:19.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like remote health care
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.61,0:34:24.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, it could really be done
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.47,0:34:26.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't fan the flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.11,0:34:28.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Should we try a crowdfunding campaign?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.11,0:34:38.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is everyone's theories
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.49,0:34:40.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.16,0:34:47.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They always do this "so that's it~" type line
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.43,0:34:50.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But then they never do it here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.12,0:34:52.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We can't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.07,0:34:53.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're not being paid enough
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.96,0:34:56.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.07,0:34:56.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's no way to cash in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.78,0:35:00.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It may be a bit sudden. Do you know the program "Home Alone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.33,0:35:02.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.81,0:35:07.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time we bring a theory related to this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.85,0:35:12.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is at least one lone store in every industry
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.74,0:35:14.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What industry?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.90,0:35:16.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the case of stores, do public restrooms count?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.99,0:35:17.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It would be strange to count that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.75,0:35:17.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not really
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.04,0:35:20.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who pays money for public toilets?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.76,0:35:22.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that's it~
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.46,0:35:26.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is, so that's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.67,0:35:30.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.68,0:35:34.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His old age is super obvious! \N -Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.23,0:35:36.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,White hair has spread upward
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.88,0:35:39.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,More and more... eroded. \N -The amount is becoming more
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.82,0:35:42.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll become all white at some point, please look forward to it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.95,0:35:50.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,, There is at least one lone store in every industry
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.92,0:35:51.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.99,0:35:54.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Lone Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.02,0:36:01.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This store is located in Kiwa-cho, Kumano City, Mie Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.94,0:36:07.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At a glance, only this store seems to be located away from the hustle and bustle of the place
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.72,0:36:11.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As a restaurant there is no more inconvenient location than this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.16,0:36:19.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we took a bus from the nearest station and walked along the mountain road for 1.5 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.32,0:36:25.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After getting off the bus, you have to walk along the road with almost no street lights for about 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.24,0:36:26.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also gotta walk!?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.66,0:36:28.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this really the right path?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.10,0:36:34.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At first it was a bit hard to believe that there was really a restaurant here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.20,0:36:36.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.  \N-Is it really a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.56,0:36:37.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.65,0:36:39.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.00,0:36:41.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But there is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.67,0:36:45.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the Lone Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.48,0:36:48.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The name is Mizuwari
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.08,0:36:50.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,These people must have been drinking and driving, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.21,0:36:51.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.35,0:36:53.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They'll call a chauffeur to pick them up.\N -Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.64,0:36:56.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hurry in and see...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.94,0:37:02.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks busy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.66,0:37:06.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just the right amount of business
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.47,0:37:11.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why did you open a restaurant in the deep mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.21,0:37:12.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it is opened in a place where people live
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.94,0:37:16.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the door opens and closes, the karaoke sound will be heard outside
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.58,0:37:19.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the city its okay, but countryside people go to bed early
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.95,0:37:23.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think sooner or later we'd receive complaints
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.49,0:37:27.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, if it is in a quiet street
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.13,0:37:30.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The sound from this house would be quite attention-grabbing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.26,0:37:34.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the lone vintage store
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.36,0:37:41.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This store is located in Tahito-cho, Iwaki City, Fukushima Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.52,0:37:46.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,30 minutes drive from the nearest station in the direction of the mountain road
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.79,0:37:50.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Through the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.24,0:37:58.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is General Store Tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.04,0:38:03.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,American workwear-based vintage store
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.74,0:38:07.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And a buyer's store dealing in vintage goods
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.00,0:38:11.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Originally I didn't want to open a store
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.83,0:38:15.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wanted to have a garage where I can park a bus
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.44,0:38:17.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then how did it become a store?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.81,0:38:22.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because I have a bunch of vintage clothing myself
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.45,0:38:25.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For the sake of display, I wanted to hang them all up
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.82,0:38:29.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Acquaintances or friends who come often said they wanted stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.62,0:38:32.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it became a store
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.22,0:38:36.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the Lone Pachinko Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.24,0:38:44.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This store is located in Kanzu Island, Izu Islands, Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.80,0:38:47.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Population is about 1800 people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.76,0:38:51.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An island where most of the islanders are engaged in fishing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.49,0:38:55.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,30 minutes drive from Kanzu Island Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.88,0:38:58.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the village's periphery is a solitary presence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.47,0:38:59.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.30,0:39:03.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.04,0:39:07.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The only pachinko parlor on the island, Oasis
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.12,0:39:11.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.94,0:39:13.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.73,0:39:15.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today the customers
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.22,0:39:18.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are just one
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.04,0:39:24.94,special_Wed_X - 竖向,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\fad(100,0)\pos(96,536)\blur4}Why open in such an isolated place?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.77,0:39:24.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A pachinko store itself should be opened in a more prosperous place
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.96,0:39:26.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But if you open in the center of the island
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.78,0:39:31.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'll be easy for people's wives to see them playing there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.55,0:39:33.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it happened like this because of that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.52,0:39:40.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you open in a quiet place, customers have less attention on them
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.49,0:39:42.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the reason to exist on an isolated island
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.94,0:39:45.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Moved here 20 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.30,0:39:49.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the sky is clear, fishermen are out at sea to work
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.30,0:39:51.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If so, its complete empty
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.80,0:39:58.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The business is barely viable
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.49,0:40:01.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the Lone Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.23,0:40:09.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Located in Toga Village, Nanto City, Toyama Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.07,0:40:13.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surrounded by mountains and lakes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.89,0:40:16.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No other buildings are visible at all
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.92,0:40:19.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Supreme solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.34,0:40:24.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The only way to get to the hotel is by boat
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.10,0:40:29.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A 30-minute boat ride in a green landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.35,0:40:34.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After boarding the private dock
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.45,0:40:41.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You reach the Omaki Onsen Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.42,0:40:46.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Originally there was a village near here
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.51,0:40:49.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But due to the construction of the dam it was flooded
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.26,0:40:55.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, only the hot spring hotel has been preserved
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.97,0:40:58.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's pretty hard to get here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.33,0:41:00.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is the approximate number of guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.64,0:41:05.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've been featured in many mystery tv dramas
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.74,0:41:09.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So guests come now and then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.03,0:41:12.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An isolated location
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.31,0:41:15.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A perfect setting for a murder
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.39,0:41:17.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's easy to kill people
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.95,0:41:19.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not easy to be noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.14,0:41:24.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has become a popular secret place to stay for those inclined
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.20,0:41:29.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The only thing is, as a place to stay, there are no roads around it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.49,0:41:33.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In addition to the place where you live, you can not get out at all
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.74,0:41:36.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the Lone Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.27,0:41:44.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Located in Genkai-cho, Higashi Matsuura Sur, Saga Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.32,0:41:50.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This store is also completely unconnected to the local community
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.17,0:41:54.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A place that cannot be reached by land
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.94,0:42:01.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the owner has to go to the port to meet the customers who have made reservations
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.48,0:42:07.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is physically impossible to have guests just coming to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.04,0:42:13.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, a 10-minute sea cruise by shuttle boat
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.53,0:42:20.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Opened in a place surrounded by sea and mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.52,0:42:25.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The placed is called Gyosanjin
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.64,0:42:29.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Both owners are fishermen
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.89,0:42:34.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because he wanted to eat freshly caught fish
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.89,0:42:38.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He opened this restaurant next to his house 14 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.80,0:42:41.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a lot of trouble to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.77,0:42:43.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can guests come?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.54,0:42:48.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saturday and Sunday, there is no way this year
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.41,0:42:50.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Day and night are fully booked
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.09,0:42:55.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Weekends are already full up until next March
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.02,0:42:59.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All working days before November are also full
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.19,0:42:56.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super popular
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.52,0:43:04.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A super popular restaurant that even the regional Michelin guide has introduced
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.06,0:43:08.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do celebrities come to eat privately?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.20,0:43:09.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.33,0:43:12.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like who?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.70,0:43:14.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Carlos Ghosn
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.70,0:43:14.60,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}*Carlos Ghosn: Former CEO of Nissan, who was arrested by Japanese police in 2018 on suspicion of huge financial crimes Absconded to Lebanon in late 2019
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.13,0:43:18.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.87,0:43:18.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Last is the Lone Batting Practice Centre
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.01,0:43:26.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Located in Kumano-cho, Aki-gun, Hiroshima
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.31,0:43:30.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Leaving the city from the nearest station
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.39,0:43:33.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its a 15 minute drive along the mountain road
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.59,0:43:42.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This facility with a huge parking lot is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.08,0:43:47.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Aki Batting Center
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.79,0:43:54.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We asked the hammer-throwing turtle owner from Mario about the business
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.18,0:43:56.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The turtle that can throw a lot of hammers
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.51,0:44:00.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do customers come in large numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.05,0:44:04.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Usually 0, but at most 7~8 people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.02,0:44:08.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are only about 20 people at most on weekends
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.70,0:44:13.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, there was only one customer on this day
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.43,0:44:17.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it sustainable?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.80,0:44:22.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The debt is astronomical, so it is difficult to maintain
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.47,0:44:24.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.14,0:44:26.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All together about 300 million
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.84,0:44:28.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.01,0:44:29.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In addition to this batting practice center
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.75,0:44:31.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.11,0:44:32.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.45,0:44:37.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H250EED&}In summary\N{\r}We found some
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.19,0:44:39.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What else is there to say
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.53,0:44:46.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada was very interested in the lonely restaurant just now
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.00,0:44:47.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have an opinion or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.18,0:44:50.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.27,0:44:51.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.94,0:44:52.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.68,0:44:54.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To drink
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.10,0:44:56.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, it's all watered down (Mizuwari)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.89,0:44:58.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.41,0:44:59.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super watered down
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.78,0:45:00.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's no good
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.84,0:45:02.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, its almost water
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.04,0:45:03.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.75,0:45:05.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's water (mizu) in watered down, its fine
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.35,0:45:06.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.55,0:45:08.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's water, its the same
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.68,0:45:09.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not a restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.35,0:45:14.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They have a driver, dont worry
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.42,0:45:15.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A lone driver
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.99,0:45:19.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I'm going to have a drink."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.50,0:45:21.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"You come and pick me up later"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.63,0:45:22.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An older woman
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.26,0:45:24.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, call the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:25.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She has sons
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.97,0:45:26.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it's like this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.62,0:45:27.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, that's right
